{"tid":2135694,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"二手車&上會問題","createTime":"2020-08-01T15:16:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-07T03:51:50.000Z","uid":342654,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0bee38db76df3f1fb70480fc06a7bb6b5ad0d817","tid":2135694,"uid":342654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T15:16:40.000Z","msg":"早排去睇二手車，睇到幾部啱budget嘅（窮L買車返工代步）：<br />\n<br />\n（1）Volkswagen Golf 1.4 TSI 2014<br />\n（2）Audi A3 1.4T Sportback 2014<br />\n（3）Toyota Prius Hybrid 2013<br />\n上高3部價錢差唔多，想問下各位巴打會點選？<br />\n<br />\n另外，想問下大家知唔知如果想上足5年會，其實上高2013/14嘅車上唔上到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25b705b0ff2c19458c51c9a4a4d1523461264c13","tid":2135694,"uid":277374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T15:19:47.000Z","msg":"自己鍾意邊架就揀邊架啦<br />\n<br />\n上到，無問題。"},{"pid":"b371cb024fb5c1edaed4733e667e505731443a89","tid":2135694,"uid":169530,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T15:19:50.000Z","msg":"呢啲車就唔好搞上會啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n問銀行借錢仲好<br />\n又唔洗比人扣起本牌簿<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d33220cad922e5b7342534d2da60b6703530391","tid":2135694,"uid":169530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T15:24:02.000Z","msg":"利申 Prius最好 夠哂慳油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63eacc09ef91e854418f3209e3cbeba20f1ffb2e","tid":2135694,"uid":342654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d33220cad922e5b7342534d2da60b6703530391","tid":2135694,"uid":169530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T15:24:02.000Z","msg":"利申 Prius最好 夠哂慳油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T15:29:16.000Z","msg":"巴打點睇Audi果部<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"9d6abb547a8601c2eddae93465371dc616824256","tid"